title: PancakeSwap, solution for users at IFO BERRY.
body: Many users participated in the IFO of the BERRY Token and received 0.00000000000000001 BRY, which caused losses in the payment of commissions, it is proposed that these affected users are rewarded by PancakeSwap with the return of commissions or some other reward.
choices: I agree with the return of commissions.
Reward affected users with any rewards.
Do not give any rewards to affected users.
author: 0xb04fDA1603626d41B4a71D0Cb52D86Aa222b31cE
